\setline{3}\linenumannotation{c}\edtext{nādāś caiva}{\Bfootnote{em. BIRCH: \textit{nadā nadyaḥ} Ms, \textit{nadāś caiva} Pts}} samudrāś ca \linenumannotation{d}bhuvanāni caturdaśa ||3||}{\lemma{\textbf{Ci}}\Afootnote{vgl. Pts S. 85: prakṛtiḥ puruṣo dehe brahmā viṣṇu śivas tathā | nadāś caiva samudrāś ca bhuvanāni caturdaśa |}}\&
