%JB:Saṃvyāpya seems wrong. The sūrya is supposed to be situated at the base of the central channel. C.f. Amṛtasiddhi - madhyamāmūlasaṃsthāne tiṣṭhati sūryamaṇḍalaḥ || 4.1ab


